data.description: Come view this beautiful Kirbor Homes townhouse in the sought-after Huntington neighborhood. The 1st floor features a beautiful open floor plan, 9' ceilings, lots of natural light and luxury vinyl plank flooring. Enjoy making meals in this kitchen with walk-in pantry,  gorgeous countertops, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and plenty of cabinet space. Relax in your master bedroom that has plenty of space for a king sized bed, walk-in closet and master bathroom with dual vanities. The neighborhood offers playgrounds, miles of natural trails, sidewalks and dog park. Located near Langley AFB, Ft. Eustis, I-64, shopping, entertainment and more!
